--- !u!1001 &7161748779991043548
PrefabInstance:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  serializedVersion: 2
  m_Modification:
    serializedVersion: 3
    m_TransformParent: {fileID: 0}
    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 998745150500815238, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Enabled
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: title
      value: Preparations for *Letters Smugged*
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: content
      value: Distribute the food from the wharehouses. The famine is coming soon.
        We need these supplies to keep the nobility alive.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: npcName
      value: Agent A
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: objective
      value: Deliver this letter from the Governor to Henry III. He is in the Governor's
        castle.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: oneAndDone
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: enableLetter
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: receiverName
      value: Noble Henry III
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: startAlerted
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: enableDialogue
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: enableMovement
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: tamperedContent
      value: I've decided that it will in best interest for the respublic if we evenly
        distribute the food among the citizens before the famine.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueSetCount
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: transactionDialogue
      value: He resides in the Governor's castle. Head there and give it to him.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogue1.Array.size
      value: 4
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogue1.Array.data[0]'
      value: Hey you!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogue1.Array.data[1]'
      value: You're just who I'm looking for.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogue1.Array.data[2]'
      value: You're the only one left...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogue1.Array.data[3]'
      value: Anyway, take this letter from the Governor to Noble Henry III.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2913163817265418663, guid: f26c40c74954afb4d9de004927a5ba54, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogue1.Array.data[4]'
      value: He resides in the Governor's castle. Head there and give it to him.
